<collectingCountry box="[1244,1315,1608,1634]" name="China" pageId="7" pageNumber="178">China</collectingCountry>
. It grows in valleys, on rocks and along road banks at an elevation of ca. 
<quantity box="[817,933,1643,1670]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="7.5" metricValueMax="10.0" metricValueMin="5.0" pageId="7" pageNumber="178" unit="m" value="75.0" valueMax="100.0" valueMin="50.0">
50– 
<specimenCount box="[860,933,1643,1670]" pageId="7" pageNumber="178" type="generic">100 m</specimenCount>
</quantity>
.
</paragraph>
